trans-unit.source: Represents an attribute of a toolbox item.
trans-unit.target: 表示工具箱项的属性。

trans-unit.source: The ToolboxItemAttribute class provides a way to specify an attribute for a <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem>.
trans-unit.target: ToolboxItemAttribute 类提供了一种<xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem>。</xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem>为指定属性的方法

trans-unit.source: In addition to what the <xref:System.Attribute> class provides, this class of object stores the type of the toolbox item.
trans-unit.target: 除了什么<xref:System.Attribute>类提供，此类对象存储工具箱项的类型。</xref:System.Attribute>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.ToolboxItemAttribute"></xref> class and specifies whether to use default initialization values.
trans-unit.target: 初始化的新实例<xref href="System.ComponentModel.ToolboxItemAttribute"></xref>类并指定是否使用默认初始化值。

trans-unit.source: By default, the <xref:System.ComponentModel.ToolboxItemAttribute.ToolboxItemType%2A> property is set to <xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem>.
trans-unit.target: 默认情况下，<xref:System.ComponentModel.ToolboxItemAttribute.ToolboxItemType%2A>属性设置为<xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem>。</xref:System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem> </xref:System.ComponentModel.ToolboxItemAttribute.ToolboxItemType%2A>

trans-unit.source: This constructor expects the `toolboxItemTypeName` parameter to be in the form \<*name of the item type*>*,* \<*name of the assembly*> (for example, System.Drawing.Design.ToolboxItem, System.Drawing.Design).
